reviewText:
This is a total dog!  Very deceiving , more content on cover than DVD.  Nothing on pop culture.  95% is in  foreign conflicts in middle east .  Cover shows a picture of the A-Team, Tom Cruise, popular TV shows, and fashions. None of these are covered on the DVD.
Please don't buy, sorry I did wish I could return it.
Really awesome looks cooler in person and a lot bigger than I thought it would be
